channel.title: [PI] Control Panel
channel.description: I have a control panel I tore off from a different source and it works fine and everything, except one problem, the players don't show up so you can use the command or initiate on them. Say I have 1 player online, it should show the player in the player selection, but it doesn't. There aren't any compile errors, it's just that the players don't show up when online. How could I fix this?
